[NOT COMPLETE, adding more as I go]

MODULES

DATABASE LISTS:

Users (Object)
	-list of friends (User)
	-list of notifations
	-password
	-functions:
		-addFriend(user)
		-getPassword
		-getName
		-getEmail
		-getFriends
		-search(name)
		-addNotification(fromUser, typeOfNote)
		
		
Profiles (Object)
	-has an associated User
	-list of posts on the profile
	-functions:
		-addPost(Object Post)
		-assignUser(Object user)

Post (Object)
	-content
	-has an associated user
	-visibility setting
	-list of comments
	-functions:
		-changeVisibility(setting)
		-getComments
		-edit(content)
	
Comment (Object)
	-content
	-Functions:
		-getContent
		-updateContent(content)

Groups (Object)
	-name
	-permssion to join
	-Functions:
		-addUser(user)
	
UI:

Login Screen (UI)
Create User (UI)
Search Bar(UI) [sub-module on all pages? not sure about this]
Search Results(UI)
Profile Screen (UI)
	-comment section
Groups (UI)
	
	
CONTROLLERS:

Create User (Controller)
	-creates a user object and adds it to the list in the database
Create Profile (Controller)
	-creates a profile object and adds it the list in the database
Create Post (Controller)
	-creates a post and adds it to the users profile
Create Comment (Controller)
	-creates a comment and adds it to the specified post
Validate (Controller)
	-can be used for creating a profile, comments, etc. takes in the type of request and checks various elements.
	-validate.newUser(user info) [for creating a user]
	-validate.user(user info)	[for signing in]
	-validate.post(content)		[creating and editing posts]
	-validate.comment(content)	[creating and editing comments]
	-validate.group(content)	[creating (and editing) groups]
	-validate.joinGroup(user)	[for check permission to join a group]
Create Notification (Controller)
	-creates and sends a notification 
	-.create(sender, receiever, type)
	-.send(sender, reciever, type
Create Group (Controller)
	-creates group and adds it the database
	-.create(content)







